<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Characteristic Species</h4>
	<div class="text"> <i>Ericameria</i> <i>palmeri</i> is dominant in the shrub canopy with <i>Eriogonum</i> <i>fasciculatum</i>, <i>Gutierrezia</i> <i>californica</i> and <i>Hazardia</i> <i>squarrosa</i>. </div>
</div>

		
	
<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Vegetation Layers</h4>
	<div class="text">  Shrubs < 1.5 m; canopy is open. Herbaceous layer is continuous. </div>
</div>

		
	
<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Habitats</h4>
	<div class="text"> Flats and low slopes. Soils are well drained.  </div>
</div>

		
